file.name: day-part.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Adzerk Management API - Scheduled Reporting
  description: Scheduled Reporting related Adzerk Management API
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'https://api.adzerk.net'
tags:
  - name: day-part
    description: Day Parting
paths:
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/dayparting':
    parameters:
      - name: flightId
        in: path
        description: Id of the Flight to Day Part
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    get:
      tags:
        - day-part
      operationId: list
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: pageSize
          in: query
          description: The size of the page to be returned
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
            nullable: true
            default: 500
        - name: page
          in: query
          description: The page number to be returned
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
            nullable: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: A paged list of Day Parts
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/day-part.yaml#/schemas/DayPartList'
    post:
      tags:
        - day-part
      operationId: create
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - StartTime
                - EndTime
                - WeekDays
              properties:
                StartTime:
                  type: string
                  format: time|HH:MM:SS
                EndTime:
                  type: string
                  format: time|HH:MM:SS
                WeekDays:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: string
                    enum: ['SU','MO','TU','WE','TH','FR','SA']
      responses:
        201:
          description: The Day Part
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  TimepartId:
                    type: integer
                    format: int32
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/dayparting/{id}':
    parameters:
      - name: flightId
        in: path
        description: Id of the Flight to Day Part
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      - name: id
        in: path
        description: Id of the Day Part
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    get:
      tags:
        - day-part
      operationId: get
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      responses:
        200:
          description: The Day Part
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/day-part.yaml#/schemas/DayPart'
  '/v1/flight/{flightId}/dayparting/{id}/delete':
    parameters:
      - name: flightId
        in: path
        description: Id of the Flight to Day Part
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      - name: id
        in: path
        description: Id of the Day Part
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    post:
      tags:
        - day-part
      operationId: delete
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      responses:
        204:
          description: Successfully Deleted
components:
  securitySchemes:
    $ref: './components/security-schemes.yaml#/components/securitySchemes'
